--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^obsMqtt
is: ^observable
doc:
  Subscribe to MQTT connector published messages
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^obsMqttConnRef
is: ^ref
of: ^mqttConn
tagOn: ^obsMqtt
doc:
  Subscribe to the topic on this MQTT connector
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^obsMqttTopic
is: ^str
tagOn: ^obsMqtt
doc:
  Receive published messages that match this filter
